{
  "total_duration": 514.074,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 15.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象你去机场或火车站送一个人：他不是去随便玩一天，而是要去参加一场很重要的比赛。你会早点到，看看他的行李和装备，然后认真说一句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "good luck"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 15.486,
      "end": 30.797,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Goodbye and good luck"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文可以说“再见，一路顺风”。这里的 goodbye 不是伤心告别，而是一次送行；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "good luck"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是在别人开始挑战前，送给他的祝福。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 31.147,
      "end": 51.099,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文的地点也要先看懂。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Portsmouth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英国南部的港口城市，在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the United Kingdom"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它和船、海港、出海很有关系。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "harbour"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是普通河边或公园湖边，而是船停靠、准备、再出发的地方。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 51.449,
      "end": 73.24,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这一课不是单纯看一艘小船。查尔斯·艾利森船长要从 Portsmouth 启航，驾驶有名的小船"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Topsail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去横渡"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Atlantic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是欧洲和美洲之间的大西洋。邻居们去海港，是为了送行、祝福，并且为他感到骄傲。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 73.59,
      "end": 96.79,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始就给出出发计划："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Our neighbour, Captain Charles Alison, will sail from Portsmouth tomorrow."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是船长，负责一艘船的人；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will sail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "告诉我们这是明天的计划。他不是从随便一个地方出发，而是从英国港口城市 Portsmouth 出海。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 97.14,
      "end": 117.339,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二步是送行地点："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We'll meet him at the harbour early in the morning."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "大家会一大早去 harbour，因为那里才是船准备离开的地方。然后课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He will be in his small boat, Topsail."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Topsail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是船名，不是一个普通单词练习。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 117.689,
      "end": 140.481,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这艘船小，但不普通："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Topsail is a famous little boat. It has sailed across the Atlantic many times."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has sailed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是它过去到现在的经历：它已经多次横渡大西洋。正因为有这样的记录，明天的比赛听起来不是乱冒险，而是一个认真准备过的挑战。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 140.831,
      "end": 166.074,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "出发时间很清楚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Alison will set out at eight o'clock, so we'll have plenty of time."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "set out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是启程，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "plenty of time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是时间很充裕。大家可以看船，然后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "say goodbye"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他会离开两个月，参加横渡大西洋的重要比赛，所以邻居们"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "are very proud of him"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 166.424,
      "end": 171.624,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课先别急着背船的知识。你觉得大家为什么要一大早去 harbour？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 171.974,
      "end": 175.826,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为船长要从那里出发，所以他们要去送行？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 176.176,
      "end": 189.612,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。send-off 就是到出发的地方，在人真正离开前见他一面，说 goodbye，也说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "good luck"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。机场、火车站、校队比赛前集合，其实都有类似的感觉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 189.962,
      "end": 195.302,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Portsmouth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我需要记住很多英国地理吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 195.651,
      "end": 204.411,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不需要。只要知道 Portsmouth 是英国南部的港口城市，船从这里出海很自然。海港就是这件事的起点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 204.761,
      "end": 207.682,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Atlantic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 208.032,
      "end": 220.536,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the Atlantic"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是大西洋，在欧洲和美洲之间。小船横渡大西洋不是观光小游船，而是一个很长、很难、很正式的挑战。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 220.886,
      "end": 229.191,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Topsail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "has sailed across the Atlantic many times，是不是在告诉我们这艘船有经验？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 229.541,
      "end": 248.637,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正是。明天 Captain Alison"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will sail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这是未来计划；但 Topsail"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has sailed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "across the Atlantic many times，这是过去到现在积累的记录。一个是明天要做什么，一个是这艘船已经证明过什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 248.987,
      "end": 254.637,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以重点不是“我喜欢船”，而是“一个人要去做难事，身边的人去祝福他”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 254.987,
      "end": 265.187,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就抓住了。重要出发、起点、装备、道别、祝福、骄傲、长挑战，这条线比船的型号更重要。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
