      "start": 376.052,
      "end": 399.771,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 不做干巴巴的 will 表格。我们把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "当成一张明天早晨的送行时间表："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will sail from Portsmouth tomorrow"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，明天从 Portsmouth 启航；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We'll meet him at the harbour early in the morning"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一大早在海港见他；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will set out at eight o'clock"
        },
